{"tid":439584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警超聯] 爆警署locker偷同袍錢歸究佔中 男警判囚21個月","createTime":"2017-10-18T02:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T05:40:51.000Z","uid":51271,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"901409bd454fa71d24f8c936f33e25f2f109cd8b","tid":439584,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171018/57345964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171018%2F57345964&d=Fp0gW9q2H3tmsIhTXVHjeQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=63905dfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171018%2F57345964&h=c47d8dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171018/57345964</a><br />\n<br />\n入警隊一年的男警在得悉同袍於警署內儲物櫃密碼鎖的密碼後，去年6月多次偷偷打開同袍的儲物櫃先後共偷去1,300元。他早前在區院承認偷竊罪，求情指受訓期間正值佔領運動，加上籌備婚禮及工作壓力等患上抑鬱，法官今判被告入獄21個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉智偉(27歲)承認於去年6月底某天至7月8日期間，在友翔道油麻地警署5樓一間男儲物櫃室，先後3次偷取共1,300元現金，及後同袍暗中在儲物櫃安裝攝錄器而揭發被告於7月9日在同一地方企圖偷竊。"},{"pid":"64826be6f36178a0c982d9ac6bbb48af6f87e48f","tid":439584,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"又賴佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n肯定九七回歸都係因為佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3d60ae7d80f9eee185e969fbd4b25604e3c109","tid":439584,"uid":609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"屌 原來個弱智警犯只係入職一年 犯案時佔中一早完左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關乜春佔中事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4ee08a75d5774a94f6cf2f9f13f79c37b0ba99","tid":439584,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"當班警"},{"pid":"dce173955673b60ba4ce3f10a984d9853dd52112","tid":439584,"uid":13724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"條律師幫佢諗佔中呢個理由嗰陣有無覺得自己on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ecbb2ccbc1a45c6a99644fbd32994e84ce8b8e","tid":439584,"uid":28367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"去年6月犯案，即係16年6月<br />\n再減去入職1年，即15年6月畢業<br />\n再減半年受訓，即15年1月入班<br />\n<br />\n我有冇理解錯？<br />\n<br />\n佔領係14年9-12月<br />\n未入班已經受影響有情緒病都請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe03b4b2aa19be4b803fda3adbafacb02eb189d2","tid":439584,"uid":51288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 原來個弱智警犯只係入職一年 犯案時佔中一早完左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關乜春佔中事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係㗎,佢佔中應該受緊訓,果陣都有調學警上前線㗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冇野搵野嚟賴都弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賴佢令壽堂做雞壓力大咪仲合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb17ca045d53c9566220c7363d1cddecf6b1cb01","tid":439584,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去年6月犯案，即係16年6月<br />\n再減去入職1年，即15年6月畢業<br />\n再減半年受訓，即15年1月入班<br />\n<br />\n我有冇理解錯？<br />\n<br />\n佔領係14年9-12月<br />\n未入班已經受影響有情緒病都請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佔中影響力好強<br />\n可以穿透電視, 淨係睇電視都會俾佔中影響到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092d16a6de36bfa3b72e5a1d2e86164491089853","tid":439584,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"加入警隊一年的男警在得悉同袍於警署內儲物櫃密碼鎖的密碼後，去年6月多次偷偷打開同袍的儲物櫃先後共偷去1,300元。他早前在區院承認偷竊罪，求情指受訓期間正值佔領運動，加上籌備婚禮及工作壓力等患上抑鬱，法官今判被告入獄21個月。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">律師求情時指，被告劉智偉(27歲)的報告透露，被告受婚姻和工作壓力影響，加上佔中期間要在警局候命，此時法官練錦鴻回應指：「即係工作啫」，律師又透露被告患有適應障礙，現已認錯知錯，向家人、事主及警隊致歉，而被告犯案不是因財政困難，只是貪念和以犯案以舒緩壓力，被告願意賠償及承擔法律責任，重犯機會低，亦得到家人支持，被告望獲輕判以盡快出獄回報社會。</span><br />\n<br />\n被告早前承認於去年6月底某天至7月8日期間，在友翔道油麻地警署5樓一間男儲物櫃室，先後3次偷取共1,300元現金，及後同袍暗中在儲物櫃安裝攝錄器而揭發被告於7月9日在同一地方企圖偷竊。"},{"pid":"b3fa6b7d487012fd8a4639698452e70d406703ff","tid":439584,"uid":38820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43ec4f516abaf6c12b9f0a4c84ea672e7b577f9","tid":439584,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"最撚衰佔中。<br />\n賴到而家都仲賴緊佔中"},{"pid":"db29155bcd0d4ad29069a43f0f7b170fe6d5c1cf","tid":439584,"uid":15863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"因佔中壓力爆煲而屢次犯案的香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831f04956488008f9d54bb1495d0e1e21c361dc3","tid":439584,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"關佔中事<br />\n向太係咪應該幫下佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cce52061b6019c724217c2957ffcc8ef3b0dcc5","tid":439584,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"少少野又壓力爆煲又抑鬱<br />\n證明佢根本唔適合呢份工<br />\n點解可以垃圾都請到返黎<br />\n<br />\n 一陣籌備離婚又抑鬱多次"},{"pid":"5d8a0274f21528faf4a879623b6e1266b410e399","tid":439584,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"精神有問題都請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ff4c7103203e3791748360011c373f2083815a","tid":439584,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"警隊會唔會學立法會追返佢d糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba49b0a3db49ac9198da86c733657086fe1f7e9","tid":439584,"uid":4990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"21個月咁小？<br />\n知法犯法判返三幾年先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5a9505cd1bf0db67b940b754a18f04b44e83f3","tid":439584,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中，搞琴我mid term 炒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4840c2f0e7ea61ac959627b1da7b098c1703da","tid":439584,"uid":36968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條律師幫佢諗佔中呢個理由嗰陣有無覺得自己on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過係隻警犬迫律師咁講<br />\n人地同係照個客嘅指示講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f968c99c6af0246dc4098ae6c5a29dfefbcc9f2d","tid":439584,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條律師幫佢諗佔中呢個理由嗰陣有無覺得自己on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過係隻警犬迫律師咁講<br />\n人地同係照個客嘅指示講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n律師有責任同個客講乜係適合乜係唔適合啩"}]}